  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Business Development Manager",
  "description": "<h2><strong>The Job Opportunity - AI Growth Manager</strong></h2><p>We are seeking an <strong>AI Solutions Growth Manager</strong> to lead business development initiatives and expand our customer base across multiple sectors, with a strong focus on retail, F&B, hospitality, services, and manufacturing.</p><p>This is a client-facing, consultative role, ideal for a professional who enjoys engaging senior stakeholders, understanding business challenges, and positioning AI solutions that deliver real operational and commercial value.</p><h2><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Develop new customer opportunities across:</p><ul><li><p>Retail, F&B, service and hospitality sectors (AI Sales, Concierge & Service Agents)</p></li><li><p>Manufacturing and industrial sectors (AI Trainer Agent)</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Conduct discovery discussions with organisations to understand:</p><ul><li><p>Service and operational challenges</p></li><li><p>Productivity and workforce training gaps</p></li><li><p>Customer engagement and conversion opportunities</p></li><li><p>Areas where AI can improve bottom-line performance</p></li></ul></li><li><p>Drive business development activities including lead generation, prospect engagement, and relationship building</p></li><li><p>Secure and qualify demo appointments with key decision makers</p></li><li><p>Position our company  Aitom AI as a trusted, practical and scalable AI solution, aligned to customer needs</p></li><li><p>Work closely with internal solution and technical teams to support successful engagements</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Who We Are Looking For</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Background in business development, sales, account management, or client engagement</p></li><li><p>Comfortable engaging business owners, senior managers, and functional leaders</p></li><li><p>Strong communication and interpersonal skills with a professional, confident presence</p></li><li><p>Commercially minded with the ability to link solutions to business outcomes</p></li><li><p>Experience in retail, hospitality, services, manufacturing, SaaS or enterprise solutions is an advantage</p></li><li><p>Exposure to AI, digital transformation or technology solutions is a plus, but not mandatory</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Why Join Us</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Be part of a growing AI solutions business with <strong>locally developed technology</strong></p></li><li><p>Sell <strong>practical, real-world AI solutions</strong>, not experimental concepts</p></li><li><p>Strong management and technical support</p></li><li><p>Clear growth pathway into senior commercial or strategic roles</p></li><li><p>Competitive remuneration with performance-based incentives</p></li><li><p>High-visibility role with autonomy and trust</p></li></ul><p></p>",
